snippet.title: Wacky Waiters for the Commodore VIC-20 / Commodore VC-20
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

You are controlling a waiter and have to hop from one side of the screen to the other and back again hopping in and out of lifts trying not to spill the drinks tray the waiter is carrying to the beckoning customer on the opposite side of the screen.
